a, Kumamoto|Yamaga]] and [[Nagomi, Kumamoto|Nagomi]]||[[Kumamoto Prefectural Ancient Burial Mound Museum]] |- | {{Interlanguage link multi|Usa Fudoki no Oka|ja|3=宇佐風土記の丘|lt=Usa Fudoki no Oka}}||[[Ōita Prefecture|Ōita]] || [[Bungo Province|Bungo]]||[[Usa, Ōita|Usa]]||[[Ōita Prefectural Museum of History]] |- | Saitobaru Fudoki no Oka||[[Miyazaki Prefecture|Miyazaki]] || [[Hyūga Province|Hyūga]] ||[[Saito, Miyazaki|Saito]]||Miyazaki Prefectural Saitobaru Archaeological Museum |-
