A '''Natin''' ({{lang-he|נתין}}) is an alleged descendant of the [[Gibeonites]]. In [[Judaism]], special regulations apply to such people; they are not, for example, traditionally permitted to marry ordinary [[Jews]] ([[Yebamot]], 8:3). For more information, see also [[Nethinim]].


